..  .. _`PR #4588`: https://github.com/leo-editor/leo-editor/pull/4588

..  - `PR #4464`_ and `PR #4588`_: Fix abbreviation bugs.

**Enhancements**


**Settings**


**Code Improvements**

- Significant preformance improvements.
- More concrete type annotations.
- Remove the confusion between wrappers and widgets.</t>
